    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆特点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《ABYSS SEEKER》是一款双摇杆生存射击游戏，玩家通过双摇杆自由控制角色，在限制时间内在大量敌人中生存下来，并击败最后一波中出现的Boss，进入下一个地下城。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/8dbbb737e970a475117f007193b3cc55.poster.avif?t=1738933205\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/8dbbb737e970a475117f007193b3cc55.webm?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/8dbbb737e970a475117f007193b3cc55.mp4?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>玩家角色发射的射击可以通过升级时出现的自定义道具自由组合，改变其特性，用“独一无二的射击”战斗。击败接踵而来的黑暗军势，成功生还吧！ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/a8c762144d0bb4ab7c94b497e3b517ea.poster.avif?t=1738933205\" width=800 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/a8c762144d0bb4ab7c94b497e3b517ea.webm?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/a8c762144d0bb4ab7c94b497e3b517ea.mp4?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※ 本作是以《HEAVEN SEEKER 残酷世界的拯救之道》为题材的衍生作品。本作品单独也可以尽情享受。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><strong>◆更强大的Boss</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受到深渊影响的个体，类似于曾在天空城出现的区域Boss，变得更加强大，并会袭击进入地下城的冒险者。躲避Boss释放的弹幕，努力将其讨伐吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/fc8b908592a785ac7a599892353d03a1.poster.avif?t=1738933205\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/fc8b908592a785ac7a599892353d03a1.webm?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/fc8b908592a785ac7a599892353d03a1.mp4?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/3a601c423308c1b248edddc67d837159.poster.avif?t=1738933205\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/3a601c423308c1b248edddc67d837159.webm?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211460/extras/3a601c423308c1b248edddc67d837159.mp4?t=1738933205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><br>◆故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个世界，名为潘塔盖亚的地方，存在着传说中隐藏着秘密的天空城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从五个世界转移而来的五个国家的国主们，希望能够返回原本的世界，便派遣了探索者（天堂探索者）进入天空城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这座天空城里，突然出现了第六位探索者。与此同时，一个神秘的地下城门也随之显现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她失去了记忆，唯一记得的就是，她必须前往深渊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过进入通向地下的城门，似乎可以抵达深渊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就这样，她踏上了通往深渊的旅程。</p>",
